quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  104,1,Misery is for the slanderer and the backbiter
  104,2,The one who gathers wealth; and counts it (zestfully)
  104,3,And thinks that his wealth confers immortality
  104,4,Of course not! He will certainly be flung into the ´Wrecker´
  104,5,And what do you suppose is the ´Wrecker´
  104,6,"(It is) the fire of Allah, kindled ablaze"
  104,7,Which will rise (and reach) up to (clutch) the hearts
  104,8,"Indeed, an inverted dome (of fire) would be (placed) upon them"
  104,9,Enclosed in (a fence of) tall pillars